{"title":"贬值","authors":["天马　方成"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":10,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"贬值"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗　方成画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载：黄金上涨，美元贬值，资本主义世界正掀起一股抢购黄金的风潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你争我抢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹闹嚷嚷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金成热货，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美元不吃香！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨只恨西欧伙伴不识相，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管我美国老板受凄凉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说什么难兄难弟情谊重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见死不救反举当头棒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想当初牛皮胡乱吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸什么经济繁荣是天堂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看而今："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失业增加，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产下降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片萧条景象！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左思右想没主张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦头烂额独徬徨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕只怕祸不单行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威信继续降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这前途也，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不堪设想！……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}